{"tid":2429650,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"過度活躍青年承認管有鎚、萬用刀　案發後確診精神分裂　還押待判","createTime":"2021-03-02T12:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T13:38:33.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3e8f43f7f7ebaa84c9ba92e4c14df49a18c8b0ec","tid":2429650,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T12:52:45.000Z","msg":"網民前年 10 月 27 日在尖沙咀發起「追究警暴、連繫穆斯林」集會，其後爆發警民衝突。防暴警晚上一度在廣華醫院附近截查及進入醫院範圍「追犯」，拘捕一名患有過度活躍症男子。該男子被指藏有鎚及萬用刀等，今（2 日）在九龍城裁判法院提堂，<span class=\"red\">承認一項管有物品意圖摧毀或損壞財產罪</span>。案件押至 3 月 23 日判刑，期間被告須還柙。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，案發當日黃昏有示威者霸佔道路，於彌敦道設置路障。在晚上 8 時 25 分，警方到場照顧受傷的警員時，發現廣華醫院的閉路電視被干擾，<span class=\"red\">遂進入醫院範圍掃蕩</span>。追截可疑人士期間，警員發現身處醫院的被告，並截停他及搜查其背包，搜出鎚子、萬用刀連鉗等物品，最終將被告拘捕。"},{"pid":"a073850d8ea70669f9d578b4ec1091bdaea6109f","tid":2429650,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T12:52:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E9%81%8E%E5%BA%A6%E6%B4%BB%E8%BA%8D%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E7%AE%A1%E6%9C%89%E9%8E%9A-%E8%90%AC%E7%94%A8%E5%88%80-%E6%A1%88%E7%99%BC%E5%BE%8C%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E5%88%86%E8%A3%82-%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%85%E5%88%A4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E8%25BA%258D%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%258E%259A-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%2588%2580-%25E6%25A1%2588%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E7%25A5%259E%25E5%2588%2586%25E8%25A3%2582-%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E5%25BE%2585%25E5%2588%25A4%2F&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQAwAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=ccf96528\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E8%25BA%258D%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%258E%259A-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%2588%2580-%25E6%25A1%2588%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E7%25A5%259E%25E5%2588%2586%25E8%25A3%2582-%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E5%25BE%2585%25E5%2588%25A4%2F&h=89392225\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E9%81%8E%E5%BA%A6%E6%B4%BB%E8%BA%8D%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E7%AE%A1%E6%9C%89%E9%8E%9A-%E8%90%AC%E7%94%A8%E5%88%80-%E6%A1%88%E7%99%BC%E5%BE%8C%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E5%88%86%E8%A3%82-%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%85%E5%88%A4/</a>"},{"pid":"2790d49b977e3402a1c46059729c6f96713b3fda","tid":2429650,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T12:57:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa07be7d888505bf80343ef2ed07817c6706b76","tid":2429650,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:01:18.000Z","msg":"嚴官決定先為其索取感化、社會服務令、更生中心、勞教中心，以及精神科及青少年犯罪評審委員會報告。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，當晚防暴警進入廣華醫院照顧受傷警員，其間警員接報有人在醫院正門門外破壞閉路電視，遂到正門驅趕追截。其後在醫院範圍內掃蕩，看見被告坐在一個洗手盆側，調查後從其背包搜出30厘米長鐵鎚、12厘米長萬用刀、行山杖及鉗。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210302/5CF54MJLEJH5ZJ5O3LKM4JTGBA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210302%2F5CF54MJLEJH5ZJ5O3LKM4JTGBA%2F&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQAwAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=f2d4b750\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210302%2F5CF54MJLEJH5ZJ5O3LKM4JTGBA%2F&h=c5780764\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210302/5CF54MJLEJH5ZJ5O3LKM4JTGBA/</a>"},{"pid":"289bd496f5821fe855b5d3a3f13c5890d078c245","tid":2429650,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:03:48.000Z","msg":"精神分裂症 有機會醫院令<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e716bdd4a9f883d72ff70734e267171a987c014","tid":2429650,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:17:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dbc2c5c738cadb4a4fd0498a4f724008db4c745","tid":2429650,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:38:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}